  "summary": "I'm Stav, a DevOps Engineer at Beacon where I manage highly scalable, multicloud environments with a focus on Kubernetes, CI/CD, and making sure logs actually tell you something useful. I'm also an AWS Containers Hero, with a strong interest in cloud-native identity and infrastructure security. I come from a background in DevOps engineering and instruction, and I try to bring that mix of hands-on experience and clear communication into everything I do. Outside of work, I'm a pastry-chef school graduate and a licensed skipper. Sessionnize profile: https://sessionize.com/stav-ochakovski/",
